</ul>

<ul>
<li>Atom: <strong><a href="https://atom.io/packages/standard-formatter" rel="noopener noreferrer">standard-formatter</a></strong> - auto-fixer</li>
</ul>

<ul>
<li>Atom: <strong><a href="https://atom.io/packages/standardjs-snippets" rel="noopener noreferrer">standardjs-snippets</a></strong> - code snippets</li>
</ul>

<ul>
<li>Brackets: <strong><a href="https://github.com/ishamf/brackets-standard/" rel="noopener noreferrer">brackets-standard (⭐10)</a></strong> - linter</li>
</ul>

<ul>
<li>Emacs: see <a href="https://github.com/standard/standard#emacs" rel="noopener noreferrer">readme (⭐29k)</a></li>
</ul>

<ul>
<li>Sublime Text: <strong><a href="https://packagecontrol.io/packages/SublimeLinter-contrib-standard" rel="noopener noreferrer">SublimeLinter-contrib-standard</a></strong> - linter</li>
</ul>

<ul>
<li>Vim: see <a href="https://github.com/standard/standard#vim" rel="noopener noreferrer">readme (⭐29k)</a></li>
</ul>

<ul>
<li>Visual Studio Code: <strong><a href="https://marketplace.visualstudio.com/items?itemName=capaj.vscode-standardjs-snippets" rel="noopener noreferrer">vscode-standardjs-snippets</a></strong> - code snippets</li>
</ul>

<ul>
<li>Visual Studio Code: <strong><a href="https://marketplace.visualstudio.com/items?itemName=TimonVS.ReactSnippetsStandard" rel="noopener noreferrer">vscode-react-standard</a></strong> - code snippets</li>
</ul>

<ul>
<li>WebStorm (PhpStorm, IntelliJ, RubyMine, JetBrains, etc.): built-in support. see <a href="https://github.com/standard/standard#webstorm-phpstorm-intellij-rubymine-jetbrains-etc" rel="noopener noreferrer">readme (⭐29k)</a></li>
</ul>
<h3><p>code/project generators</p>
</h3>
<ul>
<li><strong><a href="https://www.npmjs.com/package/standard-markdown" rel="noopener noreferrer">standard-markdown</a></strong> - Lint all the javascript code blocks in your markdown files</li>
</ul>

<ul>
<li><strong><a href="https://www.npmjs.com/package/stylelint-config-standard" rel="noopener noreferrer">stylelint-config-standard</a></strong> - The standard shareable config for stylelint.</li>
</ul>

<ul>
<li><strong><a href="https://www.npmjs.com/package/standard-sass" rel="noopener noreferrer">standard-sass</a></strong> - Sass &amp; Scss &amp; Css Standard Style. One Style to Rule Them All!</li>
</ul>
]]></content>
